name: SOVEREIGN SLUMBER
description:
As he slumbered, neurons ablaze,
thoughts, worries and dreams all raced across his brow,
creasing and warping the contours of his face.
Try as he might, they could not be lain to rest.
Through minutes and years, through wars and weddings,
never once did he shed his mask.
But now, in the depths of the night,
beyond all conscious control,
his face whispered of the man within.
